title.narrative: Republic of Marshall Islands - Renewable Energy initiative

description.narrative: Facilitation and technical analysis to develop a long-term roadmap for RMI’s energy sector. Support for the preparation and facilitation of a development partner meeting for the energy sector in Majuro in early 2018. A salary package for one year for one energy advisor role in the Energy Planning Division. Grid model, equipment and training for integration of renewable generation into the grid. Installation of around 160kW of solar PV generation .
